metadata.name: ://MANY-FOLD RAW
metadata.description:
I present to you the raw sketch edition of ://MANY-FOLD. With the recent OE minting out at 56,664 pieces I wanted to share this piece with holders of ://THE CREATION OF GM3.0 and a few lucky ones as it holds significance to me. After spending years as a pepe/meme artist, I’ve always put my everything into my sketches, drafting, editing, redoing and reaching the final raw sketch before putting more heart and soul into the the final product. 

://MANY-FOLD is dear to me as it has become one of my biggest minted out collection (57K) and I wanted to gift this to holders for their love and support. While we charter deeper into MAP, i will use this drive to motivate me to deliver better quality work for me and most importantly holders. 

My work is nothing without y’all and y’all are my everything. Thank you and I love you.
